这个城市
called New Orleans.

5
00:00:11,644 --> 00:00:14,272
现在女巫密谋将我引回此地
Now, a plot by witches
has lured me back,

6
00:00:14,447 --> 00:00:16,472
希望我能打败一个暴君
hoping that I will defeat a tyrant.

7
00:00:17,517 --> 00:00:19,712
