我却有自己的打算
Despite my brother's best efforts,
I have a plan of my own.

15
00:00:36,069 --> 00:00:39,095
我会夺回我的家园
让它重新属于我
I will take back my home
and reclaim what was mine.

16
00:00:39,272 --> 00:00:40,739
我会成为王
I will be king.

17
