autumn nap, upstairs.

100
00:04:55,728 --> 00:04:57,628
去啊，四处看看
Well, go on.
Take a look around.

101
00:04:57,864 --> 00:05:00,128
导演：布烈德特纳尔

102
00:05:01,200 --> 00:05:03,327
你和我一样都还熟悉这屋子
You remember this house as well as l.

103
