-Are we interrupting?
-Yes.

115
00:05:55,321 --> 00:05:56,310
没有
No.

116
00:05:56,489 --> 00:05:59,890
亲爱的以利亚
你希望我得到幸福
Dearest Elijah, you've only
ever wished happiness for me.

117
00:06:00,059 --> 00:06:01,390
我和艾米尔恋爱了
Emil and I are in love.

118
00:06:02,128 --> 00:06:03,595
