Last time I saw you, Royal Street
was burning and you all were fleeing

335
00:19:41,013 --> 00:19:42,776
躲避父亲追赶
the city from your daddy.

336
00:19:43,715 --> 00:19:44,943
我以为你死了
I thought you were dead.

337
00:19:45,350 --> 00:19:47,113
你从未回来确认过
You never looked back to find out.

338
00:19:49,288 --> 00:19:50,550
你来这里干什么？
Why are you here?

339
00:19:51,456 --> 00:19:54,152
找以利亚
我觉得克劳斯对他做了什么
Elijah. I think Klaus
has done something to him.

340
00:19:54,326 --> 00:19:56,089
好了，别说了
Stop, stop, right there.

341
00:19:56,261 --> 00:19:58,354
从你们米卡森家族身上我学到一点
There's one thing I learned
about you Mikaelsons.

342
00:19:58,530 --> 00:20:01,192
不要卷进家族斗争
It's don't get in the middle
of family feuding.

343
00:20:01,366 --> 00:20:02,492
没有好下场
It doesn't end well.

344
00:20:02,668 --> 00:20:05,228
我们之间什么也没发生
我以生命担保
There's nothing going on between us,
I swear it, on my life.

345
00:20:05,404 --> 00:20:07,531
你的生命对我很重要
Your life means something to me.

346
00:20:07,706 --> 00:20:11,039
跟我说实话
否则情况将大不相同
Give me the privilege of honesty,
or that will cease to be the case.

347
00:20:11,210 --> 00:20:13,371
我喜欢她，我觉得她也喜欢我
I like her, and I think it's mutual.

348
00:20:13,545 --> 00:20:15,740
但我什么都没做，我不会的
But I haven't done
anything about it and I wouldn't.

349
00:20:15,914 --> 00:20:17,745
- 除非…
- 将来也不会
-Not if--
-And you won't.

350
00:20:17,916 --> 00:20:21,249
我爱我妹妹，但她总是遇人不淑
I love my sister, but she lacks
fortune when it comes to men.

351
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:24,253
他们来来去去，只有我一直都在
They come and go for her.
But I am the constant.

352
00:20:26,858 --> 00:20:28,485
她是我的家人
She's my family.

353
00:20:28,660 --> 00:20:30,719
你说过我也是家人
Well, you said I was family.

354
00:20:30,896 --> 00:20:33,330
我求过你把我变成吸血鬼
I have begged you to
turn me into a vampire.

355
00:20:33,498 --> 00:20:37,298
我说过当你准备好我就会转变你
And I told you,
I will turn you when you're ready.

356
00:20:38,870 --> 00:20:41,430
你再靠近蕾贝卡，就永远别想转变
You go near Rebekah again,
and you never will be.

357
00:20:42,741 --> 00:20:46,302
即使你已功成名就，你还是怕他
Even after all you've achieved,
you're still scared of him.

358
00:20:46,478 --> 00:20:48,275
我不怕任何人
No, I'm not scared of anyone.

359
00:20:51,383 --> 00:20:53,908
要是我发现你知道以利亚的下落
If I find out
you know where Elijah is...

360
00:20:54,920 --> 00:20:58,117
你就不用怕克劳斯了
我会亲手干掉你
...you needn't fear Klaus.
I'll kill you myself.

361
00:21:01,560 --> 00:21:04,620
虽然念及旧情，但是我帮不了你
Nostalgia's a blast and all,
but I can't help you.

362
00:21:05,631 --> 00:21:07,030
还是很高兴见到你
It's nice seeing you though.

363
00:21:07,199 --> 00:21:09,224
但愿你能找到你要的
Good luck finding
what you're looking for.

364
00:21:25,284 --> 00:21:27,309
我懂那个表情，是和女人有关
I know that face.
Woman trouble.

365
00:21:27,486 --> 00:21:29,351
你这个混蛋，你知道是吧？
You're a dick, you know that?

366
00:21:29,521 --> 00:21:31,546
为什么不告诉我你妹妹回来了？
Why didn't you tell me your
sister's back in town?

367
00:21:31,723 --> 00:21:34,317
我觉得让你自己发现不是更有意思嘛
I thought it'd be more amusing
for you to find out for yourself.

368
00:21:34,493 --> 00:21:35,892
还有什么瞒着我吗？
Anything else that I need to know?

369
00:21:36,061 --> 00:21:39,394
就是她这一百年来变得越发神经
Only that she's grown considerably
more insane in the last century.

370
00:21:39,564 --> 00:21:42,499
也许就是她杀了我的人
Or maybe that it was her
who killed my guys.

371
00:21:42,668 --> 00:21:45,831
难说，除非那个飙车族酒吧
经常有土里土气的
Doubtful. Unless that biker bar
is frequented by small-town,

372
00:21:46,004 --> 00:21:48,871
高中橄榄球四分卫光顾
不然她才没那个兴趣
high school quarterbacks,
I can't imagine she'd be interested.

373
00:21:51,543 --> 00:21:52,908
喂？
Yeah.

374
00:21:53,078 --> 00:21:56,343
刚收到消消，有人在毕恩维尔公园
发现一个狼人
MAN: Just got a tip. Someone saw
a werewolf in Vionville Park.

375
00:21:56,515 --> 00:21:58,312
带几个夜行者把他逮住
Get a couple Nightwalkers
to run it down.

376
00:21:58,483 --> 00:21:59,814
把他的脑袋给我带回来
Bring me back its head.

377
00:22:00,686 --> 00:22:03,519
看来杀了那几个喽罗的凶手
也水落石出了
Well, I guess that solves the
mystery of the murdered riff-raff.

378
00:22:03,689 --> 00:22:04,986
至少我妹妹是清白的
Least my sister's in the clear.

379
00:22:05,157 --> 00:22:07,819
关于那事，我可没时间
搅和你们的米卡森家庭剧
About that, I don't have time
for Mikaelson family drama.

380
00:22:07,993 --> 00:22:10,791
你是我的客人，管好你妹妹
You're my guest,
keep your sister in line.

381
00:22:10,962 --> 00:22:14,796
我用一支吸管把密西西比河吸干
还比较有可能
I'd have greater chance of draining
the Mississippi with a straw!

382
00:22:21,673 --> 00:22:22,901
来吧，海莉
Come on, Hayley.

383
00:22:23,608 --> 00:22:28,272
就肚子痛一下
这愚蠢的一切就都结束了
One upset stomach and all this
stupid drama is ancient history.

384
00:22:51,303 --> 00:22:52,998
到法语区来真是个愚蠢的行为
Dumb move comin' into the Quarter.

385
00:22:53,171 --> 00:22:54,536
跟我走吧，狼人
You're comin' with me, wolf.

386
00:22:54,706 --> 00:22:57,504
我在这里已经受够了你们吸血鬼
告诉我该做什么
I have had it up to here with
vampires telling me what to do!

387
00:22:57,676 --> 00:22:59,405
啊！
Ah!

388
00:23:05,016 --> 00:23:07,280
这样对待孕妇可不好
Now, that is no way
to treat a pregnant lady.

389
00:23:08,320 --> 00:23:09,947
我真的很讨厌没礼貌的人
I do hate bad manners.

390
00:23:15,093 --> 00:23:18,620
这就是我叫你不要离开屋子的原因
This is why I told you
never to leave the house.

391
00:23:18,797 --> 00:23:21,163
法语区是禁止狼人出入的
Werewolves are banned in the Quarter.

392
00:23:21,333 --> 00:23:25,201
我本来计划好了，但你晚上出去
小蹦达一圈就危及到整个形势
I had a plan and your little stroll
put it all in peril.

393
00:23:25,370 --> 00:23:26,997
别管他
Leave him!

394
00:23:27,172 --> 00:23:28,696
你已经管得够多了，不觉得吗？
You've done enough,
don't you think?

395
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:32,100
把这些尸体像路标一样丢在我门前
Leaving a trail of bodies
like a roadmap to my door.

396
00:23:32,277 --> 00:23:35,178
要不是我无意间听到取狼人脑袋的事
If I hadn't overheard this lot
bragging about werewolf heads,

397
00:23:35,347 --> 00:23:37,042
这里每一个人都完蛋了
everyone here would be screwed.

398
00:23:37,215 --> 00:23:39,274
还有别跟我扯什么计划
And don't give me that
crap about having a plan.

399
00:23:39,451 --> 00:23:41,578
你一直都有时间去执行你的计划
You've had all the time
in the world to execute a plan

400
00:23:41,753 --> 00:23:43,380
但你什么都没做出来
and no one's seen
you do a damn thing.

401
00:23:44,423 --> 00:23:47,119
以利亚做了个交易来保护你的孩子
Elijah made a deal
to protect your child

402
00:23:47,292 --> 00:23:50,693
希望能把你从自私堕落的
自我中拯救出来
so that he could save you
from your selfish, rotten self.

403
00:23:50,862 --> 00:23:53,888
而你显然根本不在乎这个孩子和以利亚
But you obviously don't give a damn
about the child or Elijah,

404
00:23:54,065 --> 00:23:55,794
瞧你做了什么去珍惜这一切？
because what have
you done to honor it?

405
00:23:55,967 --> 00:23:58,094
我做了一切
I have done everything.

406
00:23:59,204 --> 00:24:01,536
要我一件件地跟你讲清楚吗？
Let me spell it out for you,
shall l?

407
00:24:01,706 --> 00:24:04,174
从我到这的第一天，马赛尔就不信任我
From the day I arrived,
Marcel hasn't trusted me.

408
00:24:04,342 --> 00:24:07,038
从第一天开始
他竞让他的吸血鬼服下有毒的马鞭草
From day one, he's had his
vampires ingest toxic vervain,

409
00:24:07,212 --> 00:24:10,648
而你知道的，妹妹
那是用来防止他们受我精神控制
which, as you know, little sister,
protects them from my mind control.

410
00:24:11,950 --> 00:24:13,713
我需要一个间谋
I needed a spy.

411
00:24:15,053 --> 00:24:18,147
一个和我里应外合
且马赛尔永远不会怀疑的人
Someone on the inside, with me,
who Marcel would never suspect.

412
00:24:19,124 --> 00:24:22,184
所以我赶在他之前先下手为强
So, I created a day zero
and got there first.

413
00:24:23,595 --> 00:24:24,789
嘿
Hey!

414
00:24:24,963 --> 00:24:28,831
拜你大开杀戒所赐
马赛尔失去了六个吸血鬼
Marcel had just lost six vampires,
thanks to your little murder spree

415
00:24:29,000 --> 00:24:30,433
他急需招募新人
and he needed new recruits.

416
00:24:30,602 --> 00:24:32,069
好
Okay.

417
00:24:32,237 --> 00:24:36,833
所以我把其中一个变成我的人
在他一滴马鞭草都没进之前
KLAUS: So I made the new one mine
before he'd had even a drop of vervain.

418
00:24:40,145 --> 00:24:43,740
现在我们来聊聊你可以为我做什么
Let's have a little chat
about what you can do for me.

419
00:24:45,817 --> 00:24:48,684
但我们都知道真正获得一个男人的信任
是要获取他的心
But we all know the real way
to a man is through his heart.

420
00:24:49,855 --> 00:24:50,879
于是…
So.

421
00:24:51,523 --> 00:24:55,619
我兄弟马赛尔…
不错的小伙子，你不觉得吗？
My mate, Marcel.
Nice bloke, don't you think?

422
00:24:57,329 --> 00:24:58,990
不
No.

423
00:24:59,164 --> 00:25:04,500
他很迷人、性成、自信、充满魅力
He's charming, sexy,
confident, incredibly hot.

424
00:25:04,669 --> 00:25:07,968
但老实说，他是个坏小子
But let's be honest,
he's a bad boy, right?

425
00:25:08,139 --> 00:25:10,130
跟你一样
Like you.

426
00:25:10,308 --> 00:25:13,903
而现在我需要一个好男人
而不是一个…
And right now, I only need
good in my life, not someone who's--

427
00:25:14,079 --> 00:25:17,674
被不幸的伤害，不再完整
无法摆脱自己心魔的人？
Tragically wounded and damaged
by demons he can't escape?

428
00:25:19,918 --> 00:25:23,877
那些受伤的人
不是合适的对象
The damaged ones,
they're not good.

429
00:25:24,055 --> 00:25:26,046
至少对我来说不是
At least, not for me.

430
00:25:28,126 --> 00:25:30,094
我懂，真的懂
I understand, I do.

431
00:25:31,663 --> 00:25:33,824
不管怎样，给他一次机会
However, give him one chance.

432
00:25:34,165 --> 00:25:38,864
然后我需要你告诉我他去了哪里
见了谁
Then, I need you to tell me
where he goes and who he sees.

433
00:25:39,037 --> 00:25:43,337
而这家伙
我会排干他体内的马鞭草
And this one.
I'm gonna drain him of vervain.

434
00:25:44,776 --> 00:25:49,042
魅惑他相信他的兄弟找到了自己的信仰
搬去了犹他州
Compel him to believe his mates
found religion and moved to Utah,

435
00:25:49,214 --> 00:25:53,947
这样他就能向马赛尔解释
为什么今晚又损失了三个吸血鬼
so that he can explain to Marcel
why he lost three more vampires tonight.

436
00:25:59,658 --> 00:26:02,058
你们还有什么问题吗？
Does anyone have
any more questions?

437
00:26:03,795 --> 00:26:07,060
没有？很好
因为我有个问题
No? Good.
Because I have a question.

438
00:26:07,832 --> 00:26:11,233
海莉
首先，你在该死的法语区
Hayley, what were you doing,
in the bloody French Quarter,

439
00:26:11,403 --> 00:26:12,768
干什么？
in the first place?

440
00:26:14,372 --> 00:26:16,203
- 回答我
- 别管她了
-Answer me!
-Leave her be.

441
00:26:16,374 --> 00:26:17,773
你想知道我干了什么？
You wanna know what I was doing?

442
00:26:19,010 --> 00:26:23,811
我买了毒药
这样就可以让你的小宝贝解脱了
I was buying poison. So I could put
your little baby out of its misery.

443
00:26:26,985 --> 00:26:28,043
尼克
Nik!

444
00:26:28,987 --> 00:26:30,215
尼克
Nik!

445
00:26:31,122 --> 00:26:34,523
放开她
看在老天的份上，她怀孕了
Keep your hands off her,
she is pregnant for God's sake!

446
00:26:36,061 --> 00:26:38,291
所有关于不想要这个孩子的威吓
All of this bluster
about not wanting the child,

447
00:26:38,463 --> 00:26:41,557
当她说准备好不要这个孩子的那一刻…
and then the second she tells
you she's ready to get rid of it....?

448
00:26:46,938 --> 00:26:49,270
在意一个人没什么大不了的
It's okay to care.

449
00:26:50,308 --> 00:26:52,208
想得到一些东西很正常
It's okay to want something.

450
00:26:53,244 --> 00:26:56,577
这就是以利亚一直在努力的
这就是他对你的期望
That's all Elijah was trying to do,
all he's ever wanted for you.

451
00:26:59,250 --> 00:27:01,377
也是我们一直想要的
All we've ever wanted.

452
00:27:21,573 --> 00:27:23,370
我把以利亚交给了马赛尔
I gave Elijah to Marcel.

453
00:27:25,577 --> 00:27:26,942
什么？
What?

454
00:27:28,913 --> 00:27:30,574
马赛尔很紧张
Marcel was nervous.

455
00:27:32,050 --> 00:27:35,076
一个真祖回来就很难对付了
更别说两个
Bad enough one Original
return to town, but two?

456
00:27:36,921 --> 00:27:38,684
他的手下变得坐立不安
His crew was getting antsy.

457
00:27:39,758 --> 00:27:45,993
他想要以利亚消失
所以我给了他一个和解的提议
He wanted Elijah gone,
so I gave him a peace offering.

458
00:27:46,164 --> 00:27:47,927
你竟然拿我们的哥哥做交易
You bartered our brother.

459
00:27:48,099 --> 00:27:50,033
我有计划
I have a plan.

460
00:27:51,136 --> 00:27:55,835
得到马赛尔的信任，消灭他的帝国
Gain Marcel's trust,
dismantle his empire,

461
00:27:56,007 --> 00:28:00,376
实现以利亚希望孩子出生的心愿
honor Elijah's wish
that that baby be born.

462
00:28:01,379 --> 00:28:04,542
我的计划只有我自己清楚
I am executing that plan
the only way I know how.

463
00:28:05,984 --> 00:28:10,318
如果你不喜欢
随时可以离开
If you don't like it,
there's the door.

464
00:28:14,826 --> 00:28:16,316
看我在不在意
See if I care.

465
00:28:38,950 --> 00:28:43,387
我知道你不怎么了解我，但还是谢谢
I know you don't know me very well,
but thanks.

466
00:28:45,023 --> 00:28:46,786
非常感谢你刚才的举动
I appreciate what you did in there.

467
00:28:47,692 --> 00:28:49,887
我们女孩不就应该互相照顾
Us girls have got to
look out for each other.

468
00:28:51,196 --> 00:28:52,663
你们俩怎么了？
What is it with you two?

469
00:28:52,831 --> 00:28:57,700
你说过你恨他
但你对待他的方式再明显不过了
You say you hate him, but the way
you deal with him it's so clear.

470
00:28:58,136 --> 00:29:00,536
即使你恨他，你还是爱着他
Even when you hate him,
you still love him.

471
00:29:02,207 --> 00:29:04,402
我想当你和一个人生活了千年
I guess when you spend
a thousand years with someone,

472
00:29:04,576 --> 00:29:07,602
决定离开的时候
就像丢掉了自己的一部分
deciding to quit them is
like losing a part of yourself.

473
00:29:10,315 --> 00:29:14,843
但有时这份恨意实在太强烈了
But sometimes the hate
is just so powerful.

474
00:29:16,554 --> 00:29:20,081
被克劳斯杀掉的男朋友不只艾米尔一人
Emil wasn't the only boyfriend
of mine that Klaus killed.

475
00:29:20,258 --> 00:29:24,285
他一次又一次地这么做
每当我找到心爱的人
He did it again and again, every
time I found someone to care about.

476
00:29:25,096 --> 00:29:29,226
他就把对方杀死
直到我终于不再坠入爱河
He just kept doing it until,
finally, I stopped falling in love.

477
00:29:32,203 --> 00:29:34,330
他说这是为了保护我，不让我犯错
He said he was protecting me
from my mistakes,

478
00:29:34,506 --> 00:29:38,169
没有人能配得上他妹妹
that no one was ever good enough
for his little sister.

479
00:29:40,979 --> 00:29:42,503
直到有一天他的出现
Until one day, someone was.

480
00:29:45,316 --> 00:29:46,715
河水怎么样？
How was the river?

481
00:29:46,885 --> 00:29:49,911
很凉爽，清甜
It was cool, sweet.

482
00:29:53,958 --> 00:29:55,289
我该去…
I should go talk--

483
00:30:03,001 --> 00:30:05,629
- 我哥哥会杀了你的
- 那我会笑着死去
-My brother will kill you.
-Then I'll die smiling.

484
00:30:09,774 --> 00:30:11,298
我不是警告过你了吗？
Did I not warn you?

485
00:30:11,476 --> 00:30:14,001
克劳斯，我求求你
他跟别人不一样
Klaus, I beg of you!
He's not like any other.

486
00:30:14,179 --> 00:30:16,511
你第一眼见他时就知道了
You saw it in him
from the very first day.

487
00:30:16,681 --> 00:30:19,809
你救了他
保护他
You saved him.
Protected him.

488
00:30:21,586 --> 00:30:23,144
你抚养他长大
You raised him.

489
00:30:25,723 --> 00:30:27,247
你不忍心杀他的
You cannot kill him.

490
00:30:38,736 --> 00:30:41,967
你说得对
我不忍心
You are right, I cannot.

491
00:30:46,411 --> 00:30:49,471
但是你，我亲爱的妹妹
But you, dear sister,

492
00:30:49,647 --> 00:30:54,141
需要好好地上一课，让你懂得
不要随便抢走属于我的东西
need a lesson in what you can
and cannot take from me.

493
00:31:01,159 --> 00:31:06,096
如果你知道以利亚在马赛尔手上
为什么不自己去把他救回来？
If you know Marcel has Elijah, why
don't you just get him back yourself?

494
00:31:06,264 --> 00:31:08,960
因为如果激怒了我哥哥
我就会躺在楼下那个
Because if I cross my brother,
there's still a coffin downstairs

495
00:31:09,133 --> 00:31:10,430
写着我名字的棺材里了
with my name on it.

496
00:31:26,251 --> 00:31:27,878
天啊
Oh, my God.

497
00:31:28,052 --> 00:31:30,020
我在你棺材底下找到的
I found them under your coffin.

498
00:31:31,422 --> 00:31:35,188
如果这几把古董牛排刀
是唯一能阻止你
So, if a couple of antique steak
knives were the only thing stopping

499
00:31:35,360 --> 00:31:38,557
救回以利亚的东西
那么你拿去吧
you from getting Elijah back,
then, here you go.

500
00:31:54,946 --> 00:31:57,005
我让大家都提前下班了
I sent everyone home for the night.

501
00:31:57,181 --> 00:31:59,911
今晚就让我来为你服务吧
I am your humble host.

502
00:32:00,084 --> 00:32:03,952
好吧
风度翩翩加一分
Well, okay.
Extra points for flare.

503
00:32:04,122 --> 00:32:05,714
美好的夜晚才刚开始
And the night's just started.

504
00:32:07,091 --> 00:32:08,490
是什么让你决定赴约？
What made you decide to come?

505
00:32:10,728 --> 00:32:12,525
每个人都值得有一次机会
Everyone deserves a chance.

506
00:32:14,632 --> 00:32:16,896
你骗了我
我哥哥在哪里？
You lied to me.
Where's my brother?

507
00:32:17,068 --> 00:32:20,094
你也好啊
卡蜜，这是蕾贝卡，蕾贝卡，这是卡蜜
Hello to you too.
Cami, Rebekah. Rebekah, Cami.

508
00:32:21,639 --> 00:32:23,266
看得出你仍然对金发妞情有独钟
I see you still have
a thing for blondes.

509
00:32:23,441 --> 00:32:24,533
嘿
Hey!

510
00:32:25,109 --> 00:32:26,599
告诉我以利亚在哪
Tell me where Elijah is.

511
00:32:26,778 --> 00:32:27,836
到底发生了什么事？
What the hell is going on?

512
00:32:28,012 --> 00:32:30,412
告诉我他在哪，不然我杀了你
Tell me where he is
or I will kill you!

513
00:32:35,954 --> 00:32:38,115
不，你不会的
No, you won't.

514
00:32:43,594 --> 00:32:44,993
或许你说得对
Perhaps you're right.

515
00:32:49,300 --> 00:32:50,733
但我会杀了她
But I will kill her.

516
00:32:51,536 --> 00:32:54,232
放开她
你赢了
Let her go.
You won.

517
00:32:54,405 --> 00:32:55,804
我带你去见以利亚
I'll take you to see Elijah.

518
00:32:58,042 --> 00:32:59,737
你们到底是什么人？
What the hell are you people?

519
00:32:59,911 --> 00:33:03,438
嘘…没事的
回家
Sh.... It's okay.
Go home.

520
00:33:03,748 --> 00:33:08,117
忘了这一切，只要记得我会
好好补偿你的，我向你保证
Forget all this and just know that
I will make it up to you. I promise.

521
00:33:11,356 --> 00:33:14,792
你想见以利亚？
好，跟我来
You want to see Elijah?
Fine, follow me.

522
00:33:29,907 --> 00:33:30,931
邀请我进去
Invite me in.

523
00:33:31,109 --> 00:33:33,634
那得问问屋子的女主人
黛维娜
Gotta ask the lady
of the house, Davina.

524
00:33:35,046 --> 00:33:36,479
出来吧，亲爱的
Come on out, sweetheart.

525
00:33:39,951 --> 00:33:41,145
邀请她进来
Invite her in.

526
00:33:42,120 --> 00:33:43,587
请进
Come in.

527
00:33:50,361 --> 00:33:51,658
我可不会这么做
I wouldn't do that.

528
00:33:54,332 --> 00:33:56,129
你到底是谁？
Who the hell are you?

529
00:33:56,300 --> 00:33:57,426
黛维娜
Davina.

530
00:33:58,403 --> 00:33:59,768
她是真祖之一是不是？
She's an old one, isn't she?

531
00:33:59,937 --> 00:34:02,303
没错，蕾贝卡是真祖
Yeah.
Rebekah is an Original.

532
00:34:02,473 --> 00:34:05,033
也就是说她是杀不死的
Which means she can't be killed.

533
00:34:05,209 --> 00:34:06,801
她好像也不太友善
She doesn't seem very nice.

534
00:34:08,379 --> 00:34:09,778
她可以的
She can be.

535
00:34:09,981 --> 00:34:11,949
只是今晚她对我不太好
But she hasn't been
very nice to me tonight.

536
00:34:13,284 --> 00:34:15,013
那恐怕是时候送客了
Then I'm afraid
it's time for you to leave.

537
00:34:32,603 --> 00:34:34,036
是时候了
Well, it's about time.

538
00:34:35,706 --> 00:34:37,196
我都等得不耐烦了
I was bored waiting.

539
00:34:38,142 --> 00:34:42,738
但又万般期待看到你的表情
因为绝对有趣
But I did so want to see your face
and it is, indeed, priceless.

540
00:34:42,914 --> 00:34:45,542
你这混蛋
今天星期几？
You bastard.
What day is it?

541
00:34:46,451 --> 00:34:47,440
星期天
Sunday.

542
00:34:47,618 --> 00:34:49,313
我被匕首插了一个礼拜？
I have been daggered
for a whole week?

543
00:34:49,487 --> 00:34:51,648
马赛尔，你把他怎么了？
Marcel, what have you done to him?

544
00:34:51,823 --> 00:34:54,792
现在是1887年，蕾贝卡
It's 1887, Rebekah.

545
00:34:54,959 --> 00:34:57,120
你被匕首插了52年
You've been daggered
for 52 years.

546
00:34:58,429 --> 00:34:59,418
什么？
What?

547
00:34:59,597 --> 00:35:02,623
不用担心马赛尔
我给了他一个选择
And don't worry about Marcel,
I presented him with a choice.

548
00:35:02,800 --> 00:35:06,133
他可以选择拔掉你的匕首
和你共渡他
He could choose to undagger you and
live out the rest of his human days

549
00:35:06,304 --> 00:35:07,828
- 凡人的余生，或是
- 不
-with you or....
-No.

550
00:35:08,005 --> 00:35:10,473
我如他所愿把他变成吸血鬼
....I could turn him,
instead, as he's always wanted,

551
00:35:10,641 --> 00:35:12,609
只要他放弃你
in exchange for giving you up.

552
00:35:12,977 --> 00:35:15,104
不，他不会那么对我
No.
He wouldn't do that to me.

553
00:35:15,279 --> 00:35:17,372
他放弃了
Oh, but he did.

554
00:35:28,526 --> 00:35:29,993
欢迎回来，蕾贝卡
MARCEL: Welcome back, Rebekah.

555
00:35:32,063 --> 00:35:33,690
你昏过去好一会儿了
You were out for quite a while.

556
00:35:34,632 --> 00:35:36,031
我在哪里？
Where am l?

557
00:35:36,200 --> 00:35:37,633
我怎么会在这里？
How'd I get here?

558
00:35:37,802 --> 00:35:39,565
你惹恼黛维娜了
You upset Davina.

559
00:35:39,737 --> 00:35:42,171
真高兴你们俩终于见面了
I'm glad you two finally got to meet.

560
00:35:42,340 --> 00:35:44,171
现在你很清楚自己是跟谁做对了
Now, you know what
you're dealin' with.

561
00:35:45,476 --> 00:35:46,773
这是我原来的房间
Is this my old room?

562
00:35:46,944 --> 00:35:48,241
现在是我的了
It's mine, now.

563
00:35:48,412 --> 00:35:51,904
就像这个城市是我的，黛维娜是我的
以利亚也是我的
Just like this town is mine,
Davina's mine and Elijah's mine,

564
00:35:52,083 --> 00:35:53,846
直到我想放了他为止
until I feel like giving him back.

565
00:35:54,018 --> 00:35:57,920
从前属于你，属于你哥的
现在都是我的了
What was once yours, what was
once your brother's, it's now mine.

566
00:36:02,560 --> 00:36:04,858
还有不许再碰卡蜜
And don't ever touch Cami again.

567
00:36:38,296 --> 00:36:39,490
我没喝那个
I didn't use it.

568
00:36:44,435 --> 00:36:45,732
你醒了
You're awake.

569
00:36:47,572 --> 00:36:49,005
我几乎整晚没睡
I could barely sleep all night.

570
00:36:49,173 --> 00:36:52,074
这房子活像是沼泽地里的桑拿房
This house is like
a freaking swamp sauna.

571
00:36:56,080 --> 00:36:57,479
你怎么放弃了？
What stopped you?

572
00:36:59,317 --> 00:37:01,512
你本来可以摆脱这一切的
You could've been
free of all of this.

573
00:37:03,287 --> 00:37:04,686
摆脱我
Of me.

574
00:37:05,923 --> 00:37:08,483
是啊，不过在我击退那些吸血鬼时
Yeah, well, when I was
fighting off those vampires,

575
00:37:08,659 --> 00:37:11,856
我发觉我不光是在保护自己
I realized I wasn't
just protecting myself.

576
00:37:16,200 --> 00:37:19,363
也许是因为我的亲生父母
遗弃了我
Maybe it has to do with the fact
that my birth-parents gave me up

577
00:37:19,537 --> 00:37:21,869
而养父母又把我赶出家门的关系
and my adopted parents
kicked me out.

578
00:37:24,809 --> 00:37:26,401
我只知道到了紧要关头
All I know is, push came to shove

579
00:37:26,577 --> 00:37:30,707
我才意识到我不能让他受到丝毫伤害
and I realized
I wouldn't let anyone hurt it.

580
00:37:32,016 --> 00:37:37,079
我开始觉得我们是同病相怜，你和我
I'm beginning to think
we're a lot alike, you and l.

581
00:37:37,722 --> 00:37:40,350
我们都是被逼到走投无路时
We're both cast-offs
who've learned to fight

582
00:37:40,524 --> 00:37:42,754
学会了反抗的废物
when we're backed into a corner.

583
00:37:44,428 --> 00:37:46,623
我们已经被逼到走投无路了
Well, we're backed
into a corner now.

584
00:37:47,898 --> 00:37:49,297
可不是
That we are.

585
00:37:50,568 --> 00:37:52,126
是时候反抗了
It's time to fight...

586
00:37:55,006 --> 00:37:55,802
小狼
...Little wolf.

587
00:38:00,378 --> 00:38:04,212
和马赛尔之间的所有事
你和女巫的约定
This whole thing with Marcel,
the deal you have with the witches,

588
00:38:04,382 --> 00:38:06,850
试图扳倒他，夺走他的一切
trying to take him down,
take what's his....

589
00:38:07,084 --> 00:38:10,383
蕾贝卡告诉我
你和他曾像一家人那样相亲相爱
Rebekah told me that you two
once loved each other like family.

590
00:38:11,622 --> 00:38:13,146
出什么事了？
What happened?

591
00:38:18,496 --> 00:38:20,555
我造就了今日的马赛尔
I made Marcel everything that he is.

592
00:38:22,533 --> 00:38:24,125
待他如亲生儿子
I treated him like a son.

593
00:38:26,837 --> 00:38:30,068
但一百年前我父亲从纽奥良追杀我
And when my father chased me
and my family from New Orleans,

594
00:38:30,241 --> 00:38:33,210
和我的家人的时候
我们以为马赛尔被杀了
a hundred years ago,
we believed Marcel was killed.

595
00:38:33,377 --> 00:38:37,837
我们以各自的方式悼念了他
We each mourned him in our own way.

596
00:38:38,015 --> 00:38:42,111
但当我再度归来
我才发现他不只是活了下来
Yet, when I returned,
I found not only had he survived,

597
00:38:42,286 --> 00:38:43,753
还过得很好
he had thrived.

598
00:38:45,656 --> 00:38:51,151
没想过要找到我们
也没想过要团结有如一家人
Instead of seeking us out,
instead of sticking together as one,

599
00:38:51,329 --> 00:38:56,767
他选择了夺走我家族建立的一切
he made a choice to take
everything my family had built

600
00:38:56,934 --> 00:38:58,561
据为己有
and make it his own.

601
00:38:59,170 --> 00:39:03,129
如今他住我们的房子
睡在我们的床上
Now, he is living in our home,
he is sleeping in our beds.

602
00:39:04,942 --> 00:39:08,400
他到处张贴“M”
That "M" he stamps everywhere....

603
00:39:09,580 --> 00:39:11,241
这个M不是代表马赛尔
It's not for 'Marcel'.

604
00:39:12,717 --> 00:39:14,241
它代表的是米卡森
it's for 'Mikaelson.'

605
00:39:17,788 --> 00:39:19,312
我要夺回一切
I want it all back.

606
00:39:19,824 --> 00:39:23,282
如果我得除掉他才能成功
And if I have to
push him out to get it,

607
00:39:23,461 --> 00:39:25,395
那我正有此意
then that's exactly what I'll do.

608
00:39:29,967 --> 00:39:31,935
我去找人来看看空调
I'll have someone see
to the air conditioning.

609
00:39:40,344 --> 00:39:41,333
你说得对
You were right.

610
00:39:41,512 --> 00:39:43,605
那个叫卡蜜的女孩是关键
The girl, Cami, she's the key.

611
00:39:43,781 --> 00:39:45,806
马赛尔喜欢她，也因为如此
Marcel likes her and because of that,

612
00:39:45,983 --> 00:39:48,884
我才见到了你总念念不忘的
他的秘密武器
I got to see this secret weapon of his
that you've been going on about.

613
00:39:49,053 --> 00:39:51,419
那就别兜圈子了
是什么东西？
Well, don't stand on ceremony.
What is it?

614
00:39:51,589 --> 00:39:55,616
不是东西，是人
一个叫黛维娜的女孩
It's not a "what", it's a "who."
A girl, Davina.

615
00:39:55,793 --> 00:39:59,593
她不会超过16岁
我也从未成受过那样强大的力量
She can't be more than sixteen
and I've never felt power like that.

616
00:40:00,398 --> 00:40:01,387
一个女巫
A witch.

617
00:40:01,565 --> 00:40:04,295
她不是随便哪个女巫
她绝对是我前所未见
She's not just any witch.
She's something I've never seen before.

618
00:40:04,468 --> 00:40:06,163
强大得无法估量的女巫
Something beyond powerful.

619
00:40:06,337 --> 00:40:08,362
而且拜你所赐，以利亚在她手上
And now, because of you,
she has Elijah.

620
00:40:09,940 --> 00:40:11,464
谁知道她能对他做什么
Who knows what she could do to him?

621
00:40:12,042 --> 00:40:13,134
她在什么地方？
Where is she?

622
00:40:17,548 --> 00:40:18,810
那个狡猾的小贱人
That clever bitch.

623
00:40:21,952 --> 00:40:23,112
我不知道
I don't know.

624
00:40:23,287 --> 00:40:24,481
怎么回事？
What's wrong?

625
00:40:25,923 --> 00:40:27,720
她把我对那个地点的记忆抹去了
She wiped my memory of the location.

626
00:40:29,560 --> 00:40:33,018
马赛尔拥有一个
比真祖更法力无边的武器
Marcel possesses a weapon bigger
and more powerful than an Original

627
00:40:33,197 --> 00:40:35,062
你却把我们的哥哥拱手给了他
and you handed our brother to him!

628
00:40:35,232 --> 00:40:37,496
以利亚到底要原谅你多少次？
How many times will
Elijah forgive you?

629
00:40:37,668 --> 00:40:40,398
到底还要多久他才会对
希望你得到救赎死心？
How long until his hope for
your redemption finally dies?

630
00:40:40,571 --> 00:40:42,402
我是逼不得已的
I did what I had to do!

631
00:40:42,573 --> 00:40:43,733
马赛尔抢走了我们的房子
Marcel took our home!

632
00:40:43,908 --> 00:40:47,002
这房子没有家人就一文不值
And our home is worthless
without family.

633
00:40:51,182 --> 00:40:53,173
我会找到以利亚
I am finding Elijah.

634
00:40:54,518 --> 00:40:55,576
不计任何代价
Whatever it takes.

635
00:40:58,255 --> 00:40:59,586
你会帮我吗？
Are you going to help me?

636
00:41:00,991 --> 00:41:02,481
不计任何代价
Whatever it takes.

637
00:41:16,774 --> 00:41:18,742
刚才的不愉快我很抱歉
I'm sorry about that unpleasantness.

638
00:41:19,643 --> 00:41:21,201
她吓不了我
She doesn't scare me.

639
00:41:21,378 --> 00:41:22,504
没人可以
None of them do.

640
00:41:22,680 --> 00:41:24,113
我知道没人可以，亲爱的
I didn't think they would, honey.

641
00:41:24,281 --> 00:41:26,943
但问题是，他们好像想留下
But the thing is,
it seems like they're here to stay.

642
00:41:28,085 --> 00:41:29,712
他们不属于这里
They don't belong here.

643
00:41:31,455 --> 00:41:33,650
要说服他们这一点恐怕不太容易
It might be kinda tough
to convince them of that.

644
00:41:36,460 --> 00:41:38,485
所以我想请你帮个忙
Which is why I need to
ask you for a favor.

645
00:41:40,197 --> 00:41:43,462
我希望你去弄清楚
我们怎样才能杀死真祖
I'm gonna need you to figure
out how we kill an Original.

